# Agung Motor Mobile — Setup & Run Guide

## Langkah untuk Menjalankan Aplikasi

1. Buka terminal di folder `agung_motor_app_mobile`:
```
cd "d:\Joki Tugas Aga\agung_motor_app_mobile"
```

2. Buat folder assets (jika belum ada):
```
mkdir assets\images
```

3. Install dependencies:
```
flutter pub get
```

4. Pastikan emulator Android / perangkat fisik sudah terdeteksi:
```
flutter devices
```

5. Jalankan aplikasi:
```
flutter run
```

## Konfigurasi IP Backend

Edit file: `lib/core/constants/api_constants.dart`

- **Emulator Android:** gunakan `http://10.0.2.2:8000` (sudah default)
- **Perangkat fisik:** ganti dengan IP PC kamu, contoh: `http://192.168.1.5:8000`

## Struktur yang Sudah Dibuat

```
lib/
├── main.dart                            # Entry point + auth routing
├── core/
│   ├── constants/api_constants.dart     # Semua endpoint API
│   ├── services/api_service.dart        # HTTP client (GET/POST/PUT/DELETE)
│   ├── providers/auth_provider.dart     # State auth + token
│   └── theme/app_theme.dart             # Dark theme matching web admin
└── features/
    ├── auth/screens/login_screen.dart         # Login screen
    ├── dashboard/
    │   ├── screens/admin_dashboard_screen.dart  # Main shell + bottom nav
    │   ├── screens/dashboard_home_screen.dart   # Overview + charts
    │   └── widgets/ (stat_card, chart_widget, etc)
    ├── penghasilan/
    │   ├── screens/penghasilan_screen.dart     # CRUD Penghasilan
    │   └── widgets/penghasilan_form.dart
    ├── pengeluaran/
    │   ├── screens/pengeluaran_screen.dart     # CRUD Pengeluaran
    │   └── widgets/pengeluaran_form.dart
    ├── produk/screens/produk_screen.dart       # CRUD Inventaris
    ├── statistik/screens/statistik_screen.dart # Charts & Stats
    └── ai/screens/ai_screen.dart               # AI Analytics
```
